{"root":{"data":{"id":"dgy0zphx6hc0","created":1773036521766,"text":"确认付款"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dgy10oslsiw0","created":1773036598599,"text":"本地生成订单，\n用client_id来区分","layout_right_offset":{"x":-80,"y":-72}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dgy12dpeskg0","created":1773036731190,"text":"成功","layout_right_offset":{"x":30,"y":5}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dgy14cuidp40","created":1773036886050,"text":"生成order attempt，\n尝试写入orders表"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dgy14royouw0","created":1773036918366,"text":"写入成功，收到服务器回传response","layout_right_offset":{"x":5,"y":1}},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dgy14rwsvo00","created":1773036918840,"text":"写入失败，重试时会查询\n是否已有相同client_id","layout_right_offset":{"x":-1,"y":93}},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dgy15jo7xzk0","created":1773036979271,"text":"写入成功，但是未能收到回传response，\n下次重试时如果检索到已有client_id就会\n终止重新写入，并更新attempt状态","layout_right_offset":{"x":-4,"y":-66}},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"dgy12e7fc4g0","created":1773036732279,"text":"失败后重试，但是本地生成通常不会失败","layout_right_offset":{"x":31,"y":60}},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dgy10pf7gtc0","created":1773036599966,"text":"调用sign api\n获取签名","layout_right_offset":{"x":-82,"y":98}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dgy1755quow0","created":1773037104407,"text":"获取到签名后，等待本地生成的client_id"},"children":[]}]}]},"template":"right","theme":"fresh-blue","version":"1.4.43"}